sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Content Creator
    participant WA as Web Application
    participant CDB as Azure Cosmos DB
    participant LLM as Azure OpenAI<br/>(GPT-4.1)
    participant AV as Azure AI Speech<br/>(Batch Avatar)
    participant ST as Azure Blob Storage

    Note over U,ST: VIDEO GENERATION PIPELINE

    U->>WA: 1. Select presentation + language + avatar
    WA->>WA: 2. Collect slide texts (notes > body > title)

    alt Cached translations available in Cosmos DB
        WA->>CDB: 3a. Fetch cached translated_notes
        CDB-->>WA: 3b. Return cached translations
    else Translate on demand
        loop For each slide (if language ≠ source)
            WA->>LLM: 3c. Translate speaker notes
            LLM-->>WA: 3d. Translated text
        end
    end

    WA->>WA: 4. Build SSML with DragonHD voice name
    WA->>AV: 5. PUT /avatar/batchsyntheses/{job_id}
    AV-->>WA: 6. Job accepted (202)
    WA-->>U: 7. {job_id, status: submitted}

    Note over U,ST: ASYNC RENDERING

    loop Poll until complete
        U->>WA: 8. Check status
        WA->>AV: 9. GET /avatar/batchsyntheses/{job_id}
        AV-->>WA: 10. {status, outputs}
    end

    AV->>ST: 11. Store rendered MP4
    WA-->>U: 12. Video ready (download URL)
